      • getCompatibleDataDimensions

        public int[] getCompatibleDataDimensions(int[] shape)
        For when external data is a different series of the same data shape. Returns the dimensions of the input shape compatible with the series parent, null if no suitable dimensions found. i.e. if parent is [p,q,x,y] and shape is [v,x,y] returns [1,2]
        Parameters:
        shape -
        Returns:
        datadims

      • getMatchingSlice

        public IDataset getMatchingSlice(ILazyDataset ds)
        Returns the slice corresponding to matching slice of parent, currently assumes rank of input <= rank of parent returns null if ds not suitable shape i.e. if current slice is [3,4,x,y] and ds has shape [p,q,2] returns [3,4,:]
        Parameters:
